    <p>Pre­mieres on Oct 26 on Viu</p>
    <p>Hong Kong ac­tor Ron­ald Cheng makes his drama come­back, 18 years af­ter his last ma­jor tele­vi­sion role, in Sin­gle Papa, in which he plays Ah Wing, a kind-hearted sin­gle fa­ther rais­ing his son alone af­ter his wife’s tragic death.</p>
    <p>Hong Kong tele­vi­sion ac­tress Mag­gie Che­ung Ho-yee (both above, War And Beauty, 2004) is a suc­cess­ful and sin­gle in­sur­ance agent who starts to con­sider the pos­si­bil­ity of mar­riage af­ter meet­ing Ah Wing.</p>

